These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, cola, sprite, milk, almond-milk
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, chinese, nigerian, egyptian, indonesian
5 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, rat, rabbit, cat
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, taxi, helicopter, airplane, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking water is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person drinking cola is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is the indonesian##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the owner of the horse is the person driving the boat##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the rat##1
11. the nigerian is on the left or right of the italian##3
12. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
14. the nigerian is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | milk    | cola    | sprite | almond-milk | water    |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | italian | indonesian       | egyptian   | chinese |
| Pet           | rabbit | turtle     | rat      | horse     | cat      |
| Transport     | airplane       | snowmobile      | taxi       | boat     | helicopter     |

