.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-2::.
There 5 different types of food: watermelon, pear, pepper, asparagus, grapes
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero, sports, spy, satire
There are 5 different nationalities: american, nigerian, canadian, british, pakistani
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train, bike, jet-ski
 1. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 4. the person driving the bike is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching satire movies##2
 5. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating grapes is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the british is between the person driving the train and the canadian##2
 8. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 9. the nigerian is on the far right##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is between the person driving the motorbike and the pakistani##2
11. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
12. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
13. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
14. the person watching satire movies is the person eating watermelon##1
15. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |     4     |      5       |
| Food          | pear    | asparagus | pepper | watermelon | grapes       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | sports  | mystery    | satire    | spy |
| Nationality   | american  | british  | canadian | pakistani | nigerian        |
| Transport     | train | motorbike | bike   | boat    | jet-ski        |

