.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, 7up, tea, juice
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, plum, busrot, eggplant
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, baking, puzzles, singing
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, bus, snowmobile, tram
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 7. the person driving the ship is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the bus##1
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating plum##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage    | 7up       | water    | tea    | almond-milk    | juice    |
| Food        | eggplant     | garlic | plum        | busrot    | cauliflower    |
| Hobby       | singing | dancing     | puzzles | baking | filmmaking    |
| Transport   | tram         | jet-ski      | ship        | bus     | snowmobile |

