.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, mystery, family, thriller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, metal, disco, rock
5 different pets are kept: frog, dog, ferret, cat, pony
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, baseball, rugby, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching family movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 3. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching thriller movies##1
14. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |      5       |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | mystery | sports | thriller  | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | dubstep     | disco        | rock   | classical        |
