The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, electrician, writer, lawyer, doctor
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, taxi, snowmobile, roller, van
 1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the lawyer is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person eating tomato is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the electrician is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person eating lime is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is the electrician##1
10. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
12. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
14. the person driving the train is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |    4    |       5       |
