.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-16::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, architect, journalist, firefighter, designer
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, salsa, trance, country, indie
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, pony, lizard, cat
 1. the designer is the fan of rock##1
 2. the fan of country is the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the rabbit##2
 8. the person drinking mirinda is between the owner of the lizard and the journalist##2
 9. the architect is the fan of salsa##1
10. the designer is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of rock is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the firefighter is the firefighter##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |       2        |       3        |      4       |    5     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | sprite          | mirinda         | iced-tea          | almond-milk |
| Job           | scientist | firefighter | designer | journalist | architect   |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | country           | rock          | trance        | salsa  |
| Pet           | pony  | lizard       | rabbit            | cat          | guinea-pig   |

