.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-17::.
There 5 different types of food: pear, spinach, garlic, lemon, cauliflower
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, indian, german, nigerian
5 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, lizard, rat, hamster
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, subway, quad-bike, boat
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 4. the person eating cauliflower is the indonesian##1
 5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the indian##3
 6. the german is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is between the nigerian and the indonesian##2
 8. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person eating pear##1
10. the indian is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
11. the person driving the bus is the person eating cauliflower##1
12. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
14. the german is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the indonesian is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Food          | spinach | garlic | cauliflower   | pear | lemon  |
| Nationality   | chinese  | indian  | indonesian | german   | nigerian    |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | rat | lizard    | hamster     | ferret       |
| Transport     | boat      | subway  | bus    | helicopter    | quad-bike |

