.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-18::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, scientist, project-manager, fisherman, firefighter
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, romance, animation, mystery
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, punk
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, frog, fish
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is the musician##1
 3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 4. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the project-manager##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
11. the owner of the frog is the fisherman##1
12. the firefighter is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
13. the fan of jazz is between the musician and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |         3          |      4       |   5    |
| Job           | musician  | fisherman     | firefighter | project-manager   | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | mystery     | superhero           | animation | romance  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | jazz | d&b          | blues      | punk   |
| Pet           | goldfish | frog   | fish              | hamster          | cat   |

