.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, sprite, soy-milk, iced-tea
There 5 different types of food: plum, spinach, garlic, lime, raspberry
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, blues, rock, country, techno
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, bus, skateboard, taxi, car
 1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 3. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 9. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating plum##1
10. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of techno##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
13. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
14. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the fan of country is the person driving the trike##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
