.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-3-20::.
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, pear, orange, radish, cherry
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, magic-tricks, dancing, traveling
The people have 5 different jobs:  paramedic, fisherman, journalist, writer, coach
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, country, disco, gospel, punk
 1. the person eating orange is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the journalist is on the right of the fisherman##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating pear is on the left of the fisherman##1
 7. the coach is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
 9. the paramedic is between the fan of country and the fan of disco##2
10. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating radish is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the fan of gospel is the paramedic##1
13. the person eating pear is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
14. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |       3       |      4       |      5       |
| Food          | lettuce         | pear     | radish          | cherry   | orange  |
| Hobby         | drawing         | magic-tricks    | dancing | traveling      | collecting      |
| Job           | writer | paramedic | fisherman     | journalist | coach |
| Music-Genre   | disco            | gospel      | country         | punk         | house   |

 